          <title>Doro Unveils New Lineup of Feature Phones for Seniors - Expected at Retailers and Networks in January</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Doro has revealed a new lineup of feature phones designed with senior users in mind, comprising three 4G-connected models. The Doro Leva series features one candy-bar style phone and two flip phones with clear audio, an emergency alert button, and 4G connectivity.]]></description>
